
                            About application
                            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. General information
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  This software is an LC-circuit sizing application.
  There are these calculations:

  - Asymmetric band pass L-section filter
  - Asymmetric band pass Pi-section filter
  - Asymmetric band pass T-section filter
  - Asymmetric band stop L-section filter
  - Asymmetric band stop Pi-section filter
  - Asymmetric band stop T-section filter
  - Asymmetric high pass L-section filter
  - Asymmetric high pass Pi-section filter
  - Asymmetric high pass T-section filter
  - Asymmetric low pass L-section filter
  - Asymmetric low pass Pi-section filter
  - Asymmetric low pass T-section filter
  - Collins-filter
  - Seefried impedance transformer
  - Symmetric band pass T-section filter
  - Symmetric band stop T-section filter
  - Symmetric high pass Pi-section filter
  - Symmetric high pass T-section filter
  - Symmetric low pass Pi-section filter
  - Symmetric low pass T-section filter
  - Two way crossover filter #1
  - Two way crossover filter #2
  - Two way crossover filter #3
  - Two way crossover filter #4
  - Two way crossover filter #5
  - Two way crossover filter #6

  This is a software, which does not cost money (maybe you must pay for use
Internet).  The lope conditions is the acceptance and observance of the European
Union Public Licence.
   
   OS support: FreeBSD, Linux and Windows.
   Language support: English and Hungarian.

2. Installer packages
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. for FreeBSD
   lc-circuits-0.4.1-FreeBSD-Port.shar   port package
   lc-circuits-0.4.1.txz                 binary package

b. for Linux
   lc-circuits-0.4.1-1.i586.rpm          binary package
   lc-circuits-0.4.1-i586-1.txz          binary package
   lc-circuits-0.4.1-i586.bin            installer programme
   lc-circuits-0.4.1-i586.tar.gz         binary package
   lc-circuits-0.4.1.x86.package         binary package
   lc-circuits_0.4.1-1_i386.deb          binary package

c. for Windows
   lc-circuits-0.4.1-win32.exe           installer application
   lc-circuits-0.4.1-win32.msi           binary package
   lc-circuits-0.4.1-win32.zip           binary package

d. source code
   lc-circuits-0.4.1.tar.gz              source package

3. Settings
~~~~~~~~~~~
  On Linux and FreeBSD use 'LANG' environment variable to set language of the
application. (English: en_US, Hungarian: hu_HU)

